    <h1>AI Watermarking</h1>
    <p class="description">Embedding invisible or visible markers inside AI-generated images, text, audio, or video so the output can be identified as <strong>machine-made</strong>. The regulatory backbone of the EU AI Act, SynthID, and C2PA.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
          <span class="meta-author-role">Marketing Head · theStacc</span>
        </div>
      </div>
